    "In order to address these challenges, it is crucial to reduce costs, increase identification and positioning accuracy, and improve efficiency.",
    "Mechanical fruit picking equipment can cause greater damage to fruit and branches during harvesting.",
    "Vibratory picking techniques may cause the fruit to fall directly to the ground, damaging the fruit skin and branches.",
    "Chen et al. (2021a, b) designed a vibratory blueberry picker, and experimental results showed that the picker caused 6.7% damage to branches.",
